title: Introduction to C Programming
description: Learn the fundamentals of C programming, a cornerstone of computer science. Master syntax, data types, and problem-solving.

title: Introduction to Algorithms
description: Delve into the world of algorithms. Understand sorting, searching, and algorithmic problem-solving techniques.

title: Introduction to C++ for DSA
description: Discover C++ for data structures and algorithms. Learn object-oriented programming with practical applications.

title: Basic Data Structures
description: Build a strong foundation in data structures. Explore arrays, linked lists, stacks, and queues for efficient coding.

title: Introduction to OOP Python
description: Dive into Python's object-oriented programming. Create reusable code and develop practical Python applications.

title: Software Engineering
description: Explore the principles of software engineering. Learn design patterns, development methodologies, and project management.

title: AWS, Cloud Computing
description: Master AWS and cloud computing. Deploy scalable applications, manage resources, and optimize cloud infrastructure.

title: Database (MySQL)
description: Gain expertise in MySQL databases. Design schemas, query data, and ensure data integrity for web and app development.

title: Problem-Solving Part
description: Hone your problem-solving skills. Tackle coding challenges, algorithms, and data structures to excel in programming.
